      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained throughout its life. The paint still holds a great shine, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
